Every professional fishermen has "The Moment." The Moment when they realize it's now or never to jump into the ranks of fishing. Some experience it after a big win in their local region, after success nationally and some have the urge after accomplishing so much in their former career field. 

Listen to @christiefishing's story about his moment when he knew it was time to fish for a living and go all in. 
#Bassmaster #TheMoment

node.title: "The Moment" - Jason Christie's decision to pursue professional fishing
